      <span class="uth-l">¶ 01 · Retrieval</span>
      <h3 class="uth-title">Bound to the <em>matter</em>, not the model.</h3>
      <p class="uth-body">Vector + lexical retrieval runs only against the active matter's vault. Cross-matter access is gated behind explicit voice command and logged. The agent never reads files that do not belong to this client.</p>
      <div class="uth-spec"><span>Hybrid retrieval</span><span>Per-matter index</span></div>
